title: Compendium in Wind-turbine blade theory and praxis
description:
This 517 pages Compendium in Wind-turbine blade theory and praxis is writen by multiple persons and compiled by the University og Aarhus. This is a tech book but readable for most people.  


This file can also be found on Ingenfare.com a norwegian survivalism page.
